headline: Finlay Minerals Announces Increased Budget for PIL and ATTY Projects
summary: Finlay Minerals Ltd. (TSXV: FYL) (OTCQB: FYMNF), the "Company", is pleased to announce that the approved budget under the Earn-In Agreements with Freeport-McMoRan Mineral Properties Canada Inc. ("Freeport")1 for both the PIL and ATTY Projects, has been increased to a total of $3.6 million.
